# 123Taxi – Mobile PWA Starter
Tap-to-deploy taxi booking app for **123Taxi**.

## 1. Backend (Django + PostgreSQL)
[![Deploy to Render](https://render.com/images/deploy-to-render-button.svg)](https://render.com/deploy)

## 2. Frontend (Flutter PWA)
[![Deploy to Firebase](https://firebase.google.com/images/deploy/hosting/deploy-button.svg)](https://console.firebase.google.com)

> Required environment variables:  
> `BUSINESS_NAME=123Taxi`  
> `BUSINESS_PHONE=07717640052`  
> `DRIVER_NAME=HOSSEIN`  
> `STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_…`  
> `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_…`  
> `GOOGLE_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY`
